    "description": "<strong><i>&quot; Survive a world where gravity twisted and collapsed &quot;</i></strong><br><br>The spirit 'ALPO' that lived high in the sky falls to the underground city for some reason. It's a 2D flat-former game where you have to find a way to get up from the gravity and traps of the underground city to get back to where you were.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261290/extras/c704a102de1ea95cff61c8a4a33e273f.avif?t=1675942007\" width=800 height=320 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Underground city</strong></h2>It is located deep underground and has developed a device that can control gravity to overcome strong gravity, but due to human extinction caused by war, the device has aged, causing gravity to twist up and down.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261290/extras/284a8fa72cf0ca411925768062aea188.poster.avif?t=1675942007\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261290/extras/284a8fa72cf0ca411925768062aea188.webm?t=1675942007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261290/extras/284a8fa72cf0ca411925768062aea188.mp4?t=1675942007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>twisted gravity</strong></h2>The underworld is now in a state of gravity reversed up and down. Be sure to check the direction of gravity and move.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SpeedRun</strong></h2>Speed Run Mode is also available! Clear it as soon as possible and post your name.",
